                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/27/237301566/1a06aee47a8ce07dedb1cad8d2715c48_9060730678504312302.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "December 19, 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Simply put, Akitsu Haneasobi is a game where you use hagoita to hit a ball towards a set target, which tests one's speed, endurance, and directional control.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "You can play this game alone, but if you want to cooperate or compete with someone else, you will need to find the right partner to enjoy it fully.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
